cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY 

The paper discusses the use of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) for communication in 5G and beyond wireless networks. This topic falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO) as UAVs are considered as a type of robot. The paper also discusses various techniques related to physical layer, network layer, and joint communication, computing, and caching, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and systems and control (cs.SY).
